{"tid":904001,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"麵檔師傳因曾持有利刀，遂以涉嫌藏有攻擊性武器拘捕","createTime":"2018-11-16T03:54:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-16T05:38:45.000Z","uid":196751,"like":24,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"c73fd3d8dd483390e7295b7fbf1434eb489189f7","tid":904001,"uid":196751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T03:54:32.000Z","msg":"昨日（15日）晚上11時許，一名身有酒氣34歲姓吳男子，在深水埗元州街1號A一間雲吞麵店用餐，期間胡言亂語，滋擾食客，並因服務問題與麵檔內煮麵的28歲姓李師傅爭執，李憤然擸起一把菜刀唬嚇驅趕，醉漢大驚跑出街外，到附近另一間食店躱避，並致電報警，聲稱被人追斬。<br />\n<br />\n警員到場證實醉漢無被人追斬，亦無受傷，經調查後，<span style=\"color: red;\">麵檔師傳因曾持有利刀，遂以涉嫌藏有攻擊性武器拘捕</span>，並將利刀檢走。醉漢其後報稱走避期間跌傷膝頭，由救護車送院檢驗。案件由深水埗警區刑事調查隊跟進。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n係咪會拉晒全香港廚師<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d73d8b7d8f78c9e3ed0b136ea2c5591811b88c2","tid":904001,"uid":196751,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T03:54:49.000Z","msg":"香港警察是非不分係好笑既"},{"pid":"2452bbcd5f43ce8a17d3fcba95a6228761f500c2","tid":904001,"uid":133319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T03:55:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea752484ea8f0f4ae7d3cbb88d0f0ef507d3c7ad","tid":904001,"uid":144534,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T03:55:32.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">到附近另一間食店躱避，並致電報警，</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e274f51ffd868360b975b9aeb1db271cacf33fb0","tid":904001,"uid":196751,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ea752484ea8f0f4ae7d3cbb88d0f0ef507d3c7ad","tid":904001,"uid":144534,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T03:55:32.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">到附近另一間食店躱避，並致電報警，</span></span><